ow is because he still loves tennis.\", \"from\": 5367, \"to\": 5646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5443, \"end\": 5448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0137280528729004e-23, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the people\", \"from\": 5390, \"to\": 5404}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 5476, \"to\": 5483}, {\"ngram\": \"his answer\", \"from\": 5489, \"to\": 5499}, {\"ngram\": \"many times\", \"from\": 5541, \"to\": 5551}, {\"ngram\": \"the reason\", \"from\": 5583, \"to\": 5593}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 5638, \"to\": 5644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not just winning matches.\", \"from\": 5647, \"to\": 5672, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"matches\", \"from\": 5664, \"to\": 5671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not just the trappings of success.\", \"from\": 5673, \"to\": 5707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Not just the trappings\", \"from\": 5673, \"to\": 5695}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 5699, \"to\": 5706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He loves playing.\", \"from\": 5708, \"to\": 5725, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He loves the experience of it.\", \"from\": 5726, \"to\": 5756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 5735, \"to\": 5749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He loves when it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s hard.\", \"from\": 5757, \"to\": 5783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 5771, \"to\": 5777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that is why he is beloved.\", \"from\": 5784, \"to\": 5814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 5816, \"to\": 5842, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Loading recommendation